{"tid":1256874,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急 文宣！] Twitter開始出現大量五毛洗版！！","createTime":"2019-06-25T09:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T17:33:50.000Z","uid":105668,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e4550f842087be1bf8246a73467497d2e7e94308","tid":1256874,"uid":105668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></span><br />\n<br />\n依排twitter上面多咗好多五毛同埋假南亞人ac出啲垃圾post撐警察屈示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而我哋自己人就少出咗好多post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以#HongKong依個hashtag而家係咁畀五毛洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PtNo7qy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPtNo7qy.png&h=b1f3a335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/psTonYR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpsTonYR.png&h=3fff2b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就黎g20喇，大家都要喺twitter 落力啲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">幫手tweet同retweet</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> tweet盡量用英文、日文或者其他外文出post，唔好用中文，因為我哋嘅對像其實係外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> tweet送中、中環海濱、g20、學生道歉、幫香港加油<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇ac可以開個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n如果見到啲五毛同佢啲post，見到就見一個report一個就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗應佢地，佢地bot黎，等佢地單機就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住要善用hashtag！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n例如#HongKong #HK #G20 #antiELAB #HongKongProtest，用啲關事既字眼做hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   集中推上面哩幾個hashtag，同埋用其他關事既hashtag，例如係關於政府講大話既用#fakenews，上次條動畫宣傳片用#animation，眾籌用#crowdfunding"},{"pid":"16e003f63f6458d2246b17c053225c930aefd6e4","tid":1256874,"uid":105668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2cb4f5265807bc002cb56cfba9a46a9d2fa550","tid":1256874,"uid":19609,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"班廢老撚識英文咩<br />\n由佢地用中文自high<br />\n<br />\n我地要出就出英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0500b2d3f3ceb1d714eb017f5239519213266f9b","tid":1256874,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"705c26c23358393f0c6a975091a3ea3824ba6240","tid":1256874,"uid":153722,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:05:34.000Z","msg":"大家上去打英文呀記住<br />\n咪同班五毛鬥柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febd67192b32ef747065cef0076b84f1013b748f","tid":1256874,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4550f842087be1bf8246a73467497d2e7e94308","tid":1256874,"uid":105668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"